For Siruseri player (1600,  4)(1600,\;4)(1600,4), there is no opponent with rating less than 1600. We pair him with the highest available Navalur (2450,  1)(2450,\;1)(2450,1).
For Siruseri (1873,  1)(1873,\;1)(1873,1), the best available candidate is (1860,  2)(1860,\;2)(1860,2).
For Siruseri (1900,  3)(1900,\;3)(1900,3), the best candidate is (1700,  3)(1700,\;3)(1700,3).
For Siruseri (2134,  2)(2134,\;2)(2134,2), the only remaining opponent is (2120,  4)(2120,\;4)(2120,4).
Again, we achieve 333 wins.

